summary: Completed comprehensive testing of image upload feature for football jersey catalog app. Backend upload endpoints, file validation, ImageUpload UI components, and integration with Add Jersey and Contributions pages all working correctly.

integration_issues.issue: Browse page showing 0 kits when API returns 25 kits correctly

passed_tests: POST /api/upload - image file upload returns URL
Creating master kit with uploaded image URL works
Creating version with uploaded image URL works
ImageUpload component tab switching (upload/URL modes) works
Add Jersey Step 1 ImageUpload component functions correctly
Add Jersey Step 2 front and back ImageUpload components work
URL input functionality works in all ImageUpload instances
Authentication flow works for protected pages
All existing API endpoints still functional
action_item_for_main_agent: Minor issue: Browse page filtering may be affected by authentication state - shows 0 kits in UI while API returns 25 kits correctly. All core image upload functionality working perfectly.
